criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — explicit problem framing and goals ("define and discover phase... core problem...");  
Represent — mapped logic into three Python functions and explained formulas (status quo, buyback, dividends);  
Implement — stated running the functions, storing results in a pandas DataFrame, and reported numeric outputs (EPS, per-share dividend);  
Validate — performed sensitivity analysis and quantified downside ($17B at $150);  
Evolve/Reflect — used conditional logic to recommend a hybrid/timed repurchase and partial special dividend.
